1: <pb/><e>Sb'it David jun tic</e> <pb/><t>Mamin Jehová alcn 'eli to may in mul, yujto wach'n̈j tas tzin b'o'o. Caw 'aych 'och yipc in c'ojol, may xon in chab'c'ojlal 'ayach.</t>
2: <t>'Ilt in wal Mamin, 'a'lj in prowal. Say el in nab'en yet' in pixan.</t>
3: <t>Yujto may 'aj tzwac' sat in c'ojl 'a a chamc'ojlal, caw yiclumn̈ej tzwutj in b'a 'ayach.</t>
4: <pb/><t>May 'ajtil jun wec' yet' eb' 'ixtm 'anma', may pax 'ajtil jun wec' yet' eb' chab'satl yaji.</t>
5: <t>Caw matz in nib'j wil syamnil eb' tzb'on maysch'olnil, may pax 'ajtil tzwa'ch in b'a yet' eb' tu sb'eyb'al.</t>
6: <pb/><t>Mamin Jehová tzin b'icl in c'ab', yic tzin ch'oxn 'eli to may in mul, 'ixta to b'i'an ax in c'och 'a stz'ey yet'l a xajmb'al.</t>
7: <t>Ax waln in wach' paxti 'aych yet' in b'it, tzwal-l yab'xil a munljel to satjub'tac yilxi.</t>
8: <pb/><t>Mamin Jehová, tzin chamc'ojlej atut 'a 'ajtil cajn ach 'eq'ui, 'a 'ajtil tzb'inax a b'i.</t>
9: <t>Man̈ junnjoc tzotj e'n 'ec' in q'uinl yet' eb' maysch'olnil sb'eyb'al. Man̈ in a mil cham yet' eb' milm cham 'anma'.</t>
10: <t>Yujto 'aych smul eb' chi 'a 'a, c'un schan pax eb' q'uen c'ultac tumin.</t>
11: <pb/><t>Aln pax jun, cojxn̈ej tas wach' tzin b'o'o. 'O'ch cab' wal a c'ojl 'ayin, coln 'eli.</t>
12: <t>Mamin Jehová, te'n waji sec matz in 'ejm 'a tas 'ay smay; 'oj wal wach' paxti 'aych 'a yojltac eb' wit chon̈ab'.</t>
